    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Technique of elemental analysis funamentally similar to and most often practiced in conjunction with particle-induced x-ray emission (PIXE) with the difference that gamma rays are measured instead of x-rays.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
